cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AR, cs.DC

This paper discusses the IEEE TSN and IETF DetNet standards, which are related to network infrastructure and communication protocols. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also covers topics related to information theory (cs.IT), system and control theory (cs.SY), computer architecture (cs.AR), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) in the context of ULL networking.
